2-09-25-15-40-58/\" title=\"Screenshot_2012-09-25-15-40-58\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://cdn.slashgear.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/Screenshot_2012-09-25-15-40-58-150x100.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Screenshot_2012-09-25-15-40-58\" title=\"Screenshot_2012-09-25-15-40-58\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.slashgear.com/samsung-galaxy-stellar-review-27249014/screenshot_2012-09-25-11-47-06/\" title=\"Screenshot_2012-09-25-11-47-06\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://cdn.slashgear.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/Screenshot_2012-09-25-11-47-06-150x100.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Screenshot_2012-09-25-11-47-06\" title=\"Screenshot_2012-09-25-11-47-06\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.slashgear.com/samsung-galaxy-stellar-review-27249014/20120925_120156-resize/\" title=\"20120925_120156-resize\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://cdn.slashgear.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/20120925_120156-resize-150x100.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"20120925_120156-resize\" title=\"20120925_120156-resize\" /></a>\n\n<small><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.slashgear.com/samsung-galaxy-stellar-review-27249014/\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Stellar Review\">Samsung Galaxy Stellar Review</a> is written by <a href=\"http://www.slashgear.com\">Eric Abent</a> & originally posted on <a href=\"http://www.slashgear.com\" title=\"SlashGear\">SlashGear</a>. <br />© 2005 - 2012, <a href=\"http://www.slashgear.com\" title=\"SlashGear\">SlashGear</a>. All right reserved. </small>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/kZHFw23KttoKjCjgXTt3GqopJsU/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/kZHFw23KttoKjCjgXTt3GqopJsU/0/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"true\"></img></a><br/>\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/kZHFw23KttoKjCjgXTt3GqopJsU/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/kZHFw23KttoKjCjgXTt3GqopJsU/1/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"true\"></img></a></p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/sla