	(676,'http://www.soompi.com/2012/09/29/mbc-music-core-09-29-12/','MBC Music Core 09.29.12','Soompi','29 September 2012, 7:54 am','<p>Today&#8217;s episode of <strong>Music Core</strong> featured special MCs <strong>ZE:A</strong>&#8216;s <strong>Kwanghee</strong> and <strong>Secret</strong>&#8216;s <strong>Sunhwa</strong> and <strong>Hyosung</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>U-KISS</strong> had their first <strong>Music Core</strong> performance of &#8220;<strong>Stop Girl</strong>&#8221; while <strong>Kara</strong> had their goodbye stage for &#8220;<strong>Pandora</strong>&#8221; today.</p>\n<p> -</p>\n<p><strong>Comeback Stage</strong><br />U-KISS &#8211; &#8220;Stop Girl&#8221;<br /> <br /><strong>Goodbye Stage</strong><br />KARA &#8211; &#8220;Pandora&#8221;<br /> <br /><strong>HOT Stage</strong><br />SECRET &#8211; &#8220;Poison&#8221;<br />Orange  Caramel &#8211; &#8220;Lipstick&#8221;<br />T-ARA &#8211; &#8220;Sexy Love&#8221;<br />ZE:A &#8211; &#8220;PHOENIX&#8221;<br />B.A.P &#8211; &#8220;Crash&#8221;<br /> <br /><strong>Sound-HOLIC</strong><br />Mighty Mouth (feat. Jevice&#8217;s Joori) &#8211; &#8220;At These Times&#8221;<br />VIXX &#8211; &#8220;Rock Ur Body&#8221;<br />Phantom &#8211; &#8220;Burning&#8221;<br />Tasty &#8211; &#8220;You Know Me&#8221;<br />BTOB &#8211; &#8220;WOW&#8221;<br /> <br /><strong>Volume UP Stage</strong><br />Crispi Crunch(feat. SORA) &#8211; &#8220;Men Boong Time&#8221;<br />100% &#8211; &#8220;Bad Boy&#8221;<br />ChAOS &#8211; &#8220;Kiss Kiss&#8221;<br />OFFROAD &#8211; &#8220;Be bop&#8221;<br />FIESTAR &#8211; &#8220;VISTA&#8221;<br /> <br /><strong>Who&#8217;s That Girl</strong><br />D-UNIT &#8211; &#8220;I&#8217;m Missing You&#8221;<br />Two X &#8211; &#8220;Double Up&#8221;<br />Rania &#8211; &#8220;Style&#8221;<br />SPICA &#8211; &#8220;I&#8217;ll Be There&#8221;<br />She&#8217;z &#8211; &#8220;UU&#8221;<br />TINY-G &#8211; &#8220;TINY-G (작은 거인)&#8221;<br /> <br /><strong>New Song</strong><br />BOB4 &#8211; &#8220;Youaholic&#